{
  "stem": "19218.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 387.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew what she meant by this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was fine with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, and-- and-- and-- my wife was a girl who was born right here in Detroit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was a product of Detroit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, when I found this out, of course, I guess, my life was devastated also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is already after spending with her, about nine days in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I slept in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had a cot in there, in her room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was with her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he came back from his trip, the doctor, and-- he went to a conference, I guess, to Washington-- when he came back, she lost her-- she lost conscious about-- it was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She always used to light candles for holidays and for Friday night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- I bought a candelabra, and electric one, to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she lit the candles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She still knew how to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she still made the blessings with everybody present in there, right this particular night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my kids blessed the candles too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my-- my-- my daughters and my granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My granddaughter, who was by her side all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She's only 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But she was holding her hands while she was dying, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that night, that Friday night, which was about July 7, I believe-- Saturday was 10.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Saturday was 10.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Sunday-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was about July 7, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She died on July 10.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That night, she went into a coma.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she never regained consciousness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We were there, all of us, for the next three days, the kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And Monday night, about 7:30, she went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Rabbi was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Came in every day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He said, let's prayers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[SOB] He said, read it with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
